<title>lk nrfʿ dẖbyḥẗ ạlḥmd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- lk nrfʿ dẖbyḥẗ ạlḥmd .. nsbḥk bṭybẗ ạlqlb
 ạ̉nt nsẖydnạ .. bhjẗ qlwbnạ .. wnbʿ srwrnạ
 ạlqrạr- nʿyd lk nḥtfl lk .. lk ạsẖtyạqnạ yạ ạ̹lh tsbyḥnạ
 nʿyd lk nḥtfl lk .. ạ̉nt frḥtnạ bạlḥmd nbthj bk
 2- ạ̉nt jạls wsṭ tsbyḥnạ .. tgẖmr bmjdk ḥyạtnạ
 ʿznạ bk .. yạ ạ̹lhnạ .. mạ ạ̉bhj ḥḍwrk
 3- nḥn nʿrf ʿiẓm qwtk .. nsẖhd mạ ạ̉hyb ạ̉ʿmạlk
 bqwẗ rwḥk .. tʿml fy wsṭnạ .. ṣạnʿaⁿạ ʿjạỷb</lyrics>
